thread.title: Nisa Starling

author: Nisa Starling
title: Nisa Starling
text: Been using TawagPinas (TP) for several years now. Before that, used calling cards. TP is so much better and easier, just get on-line recharge your account and you're good to go. Minutes seem to last a little longer than calling cards. All in all, I'm very happy and highly recommend TawagPinas to anyone who calls the Philippines on a regular basis.
